race.description: Merry Christmas To All From The Arc Hcp (Bm58+)
race.comment: ASTONISHER (7) led them up over this track and trip last time out to break her maiden in good fashion. She'll be better for that effort and this shapes similarly. She remains down in the weights after the claim of Nottle and she can continue to work through the grades. POLYVANOVA (6) comes back from a CL2 last time out where she wasn't far away, beaten 2.5L after sitting on the speed. Watson hops back on board, replacing the apprentice hoop and she maps to be prominent once again. Can get back to her best form and that'll see her hard to beat. COATACHINO (8) got the job done over 1.6L last time out over the mile here in a strong performance. She remains down in the weights despite that victory and this looks to set up beautifully for her. Can go back-to-back without surprising. MAKIN PROPHETS (3) is third-up now and should be hitting his straps as he resumed without a trial. Can raise the bar. DELTA ANNE (9) is on the quick turnaround but looks well placed with the blinkers back on.
